== Years of Tsuchinoto-tori == Years in the {{ill|Common Era|ja|西暦|1=Common Era|2=ja|3=西暦|4=zh|5=公元|6=es|7=Era común|8=nl|9=Gangbare jaartelling|10=simple|11=Common Era|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Common Era|13=User:Immanuelle/Common Era|qq=}} that leave a remainder of 49 when divided by 60 correspond to the year of Tsuchinoto-tori. {| class="wikitable" |+'''Years of Tsuchinoto-tori''' |- ![[1st millennium]]!![[2nd millennium]]!![[3rd millennium]] |- | *[[49]] *[[109]] *[[169]] *[[229]] *[[289]] *[[349]] *[[409]] *[[469]] *[[529]] *[[589]] *[[649]] *[[709]] *[[769]] *[[829]] *[[889]] *[[949]] | *[[1009]] *[[1069]] *[[1129]] *[[1189]] *[[1249]] *[[1309]] *[[1369]] *[[1429]] *[[1489]] *[[1549]] *[[1609]] *[[1669]] *[[1729]] *[[1789]] *[[1849]] *[[1909]] *[[1969]] | *[[2029]] *[[2089]] *[[2149]] *[[2209]] *[[2269]] *[[2329]] *[[2389]] *[[2449]] *[[2509]] *[[2569]] *[[2629]] *[[2689]] *[[2749]] *[[2809]] *[[2869]] *[[2929]] *[[2989]] |} === Events === * The {{ill|Keichō era|ja|慶長|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Keichō era|qq=}} 14th year (1609) - The {{ill|Treaty of Tsuchinoto-tori|ja|己酉約条|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Treaty of Tsuchinoto-tori|qq=}} (Keichō Treaty) was concluded.
== Month of Tsuchinoto-tori == In years where the last digit is 2 or 7 (where the {{ill|Heavenly Stem|ja|十干|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Heavenly Stem|qq=}} is {{ill|Rin|ja|壬|1=Mizunoe (壬)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Rin|13=User:Immanuelle/Mizunoe (壬)|qq=}} or {{ill|Tei|ja|丁|1=Hinoto (丁)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tei|13=User:Immanuelle/Hinoto (丁)|qq=}}), the eighth month corresponds to the month of Tsuchinoto-tori. However, this may refer to the {{ill|Lunisolar calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunisolar calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} or the {{ill|Solar term|ja|節月|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Solar term|qq=}} (from {{ill|Hakuro (solar term)|ja|白露|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hakuro (solar term)|qq=}} to the day before {{ill|Kanro|ja|寒露|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kanro|qq=}}).
