== Month of Tsuchinoto-tori == In years where the last digit is 2 or 7 (where the {{ill|Heavenly Stem|ja|十干|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Heavenly Stem|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Heavenly Stem|qq=}} is {{ill|Rin|ja|壬|1=Mizunoe (壬)|lt=Mizunoe (壬)|2=ja|3=壬|4=zh|5=壬|1=Mizunoe (壬)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Rin|13=User:Immanuelle/Mizunoe (壬)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Rin|13=User:Immanuelle/Mizunoe (壬)|qq=}} or {{ill|Tei|ja|丁|1=Hinoto (丁)|lt=Hinoto (丁)|2=ja|3=丁|4=zh|5=丁|1=Hinoto (丁)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tei|13=User:Immanuelle/Hinoto (丁)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tei|13=User:Immanuelle/Hinoto (丁)|qq=}}), the eighth month corresponds to the month of Tsuchinoto-tori. However, this may refer to the {{ill|Lunisolar calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunisolar calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunisolar calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} or the {{ill|Solar term|ja|節月|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Solar term|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Solar term|qq=}} (from {{ill|Hakuro (solar term)|ja|白露|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hakuro (solar term)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hakuro (solar term)|qq=}} to the day before {{ill|Kanro|ja|寒露|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kanro|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kanro|qq=}}).
